Class HpoAnnotationLine

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.io.hpo.HpoAnnotationLine
All Implemented Interfaces:
Identified
public class HpoAnnotationLine extends Object implements Identified
Represent an HPO Term together with a Frequency and an Onset and modifiers. This is intended to be used to represent a disease annotation.
Version:
0.1.3 (2018-03-12)
